name: UNCEASING VIXEN 22:22
description: We long for a meaningful connection from a beloved. There's a fire inside of her, one of the burning desires of passion and intrigue. It was extinguished only by the tender touch of a lover and a sweet, gentle kiss on a vixen's brow. She welcomes a paradox of sin and delightful afterglow, not worried about the plethoric declaration. There is a restlessness of an unceasing need for being wanted in body and mind.
